(34, 18, 'paragraph_approach', 'It’s no secret that we take <strong>the mastery of our craft</strong> seriously here at Niyel. As change creators, we know how important it is <strong>to be intentional about our goals for impact.</strong>We have (and are continuously developing) <strong>the expertise to design</strong> and carry out projects and advocacy initiatives that truly make a difference.'),
