(72, 30, 'studio_paragraph_approach', 'Launched in 2022, <strong>our design and production studio</strong> is the dedicated space where our creative visions come to life. Our experts use cutting edge technology to illustrate designs and ideas for change-based initiatives that drive impact. We highlight the faces, voices, and stories of the people we serve from a lens of empowerment and transformation by making space for creativity and freedom of expression without boundaries.\r\n\r\nBy owning our vision on and off screen, we create greater visibility for our work and our brand while cementing our legacy as a reliable reference for advocacy and sustainable change on the African continent. With representation of us, by us and for us, we make sure to tell the stories that matter—the stories that come from voices outside the known and talked about. By entrusting ourselves and our dedicated community of advocates and innovators, we are able to share our vision with our clients, partners, and the world.'),
