(116, 8, 'paragraph_who', 'Niyel is a private, impact-driven campaign, advocacy, and public affairs firm based in Dakar, Senegal. We partner with clients to co-create change in policy and practice across various sectors because we understand how important it is to build a better world through community outreach and transformation.'),
