(150, 56, 'paragraph_3_who', '<section class=\"kl-sect-who-we-are-2 position-relative\">\r\n<div class=\"container kl-container-1100\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5 mb-5 d-flex align-items-center\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"kl-content-text kl-text-24\">\r\n\r\nWe envision a world where <strong>everyone has the resources they need to live long,</strong> dignified, healthy lives. We aim to <strong>ensure every citizen can fulfill their human rights and live with fair choices and personal freedom.</strong> It is our desire <strong>to spark change and shift</strong> culture at local and national levels by engaging citizens and influencing policies. Because we have a people-centered approach to our work, our efforts stay grounded in <strong>the aspirations of the communities</strong> our initiatives support.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"kl-sect-value\">\r\n<div class=\"container kl-container-1100\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-6 mb-5\">\r\n<div class=\"kl-title-secondary kl-title-64 kl-title-arrow mx-auto\">\r\n<div class=\"kl-mb-lg-48 kl-mb-32\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>'),
