(2404, 228, 'career_paragraph', 'We welcome you to a team of dynamic advocates, political operatives and mobilizers. We are learners that maybe make mistakes, but never stop trying. We believe in compassion, empathy, and having a culture that is open and respectful\r\nWe provide a place where your individual views matter, and you have space to make a true impact. We offer competitive compensation, medical benefits, vacation, mental health days, hybrid remote working, fun company team building, and ongoing learning opportunities to grow in your career.'),
