(2416, 228, 'satisfaction_paragraph', 'Visibility is <strong>a priority to us at Niyel,</strong> and we want all our team members to feel seen and heard. We use <strong>employee satisfaction surveys</strong> to assess Niyel’s present <strong>strengths and weaknesses,</strong> and improve our path for the future. We believe in <strong>the spirit of feedback,</strong> and though we’re not perfect we’ll never stop trying to achieve <strong>a workforce of satisfied,</strong> well rounded creators.'),
